@page "/py-clob-client"

<div class="docs-container">
    <div class="docs-header-row">
        <div>
            <h1 class="docs-main-title">py-clob-client SDK Referans</h1>
            <p class="docs-subtitle">Polymarket resmi Python SDK — order olusturma, EIP-712 imzalama ve CLOB API iletisimi</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="docs-content">
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <!-- BOLUM 1: Genel Bakis -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-green);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">1. Genel Bakis</h2>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>py-clob-client = Polymarket'in resmi Python SDK'si</li>
            <li>Kurulum: <code>pip install py-clob-client</code> (Python 3.9+)</li>
            <li>Ne ise yarar: Order olusturma, EIP-712 imzalama, CLOB API ile iletisim</li>
            <li>Traxon'da kullanimi: Python signing service (Flask, port 5099) bu SDK'yi kullanir</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <!-- BOLUM 2: Kimlik Dogrulama -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-blue);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">2. Kimlik Dogrulama</h2>
        <p>3 seviye erisim:</p>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">1. Read-Only (API key gerektirmez)</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">client = ClobClient("https://clob.polymarket.com")</pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">2. Trading (Standard EOA — MetaMask)</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">client = ClobClient(
    "https://clob.polymarket.com",
    key="0xPRIVATE_KEY",
    chain_id=137,
    signature_type=0,
    funder="0xWALLET_ADDRESS"
)
creds = client.create_or_derive_api_creds()
client.set_api_creds(creds)</pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Signature Types</h3>
        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Deger</th>
                    <th>Tur</th>
                    <th>Aciklama</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>0</td>
                    <td>EOA</td>
                    <td>MetaMask, hardware wallet</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>1</td>
                    <td>Magic</td>
                    <td>Email/Magic wallet</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>2</td>
                    <td>Proxy</td>
                    <td>Browser wallet proxy</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

