    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <!-- BOLUM 7: Emir Tipleri Detay -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-gold);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">7. Emir Tipleri Detay</h2>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">OrderType.GTC (Good Till Cancelled)</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>Limit order — kitaba koyulur, dolana veya iptal edilene kadar kalir</li>
            <li>Maker → 0 fee</li>
            <li><code>create_and_post_order(args, OrderType.GTC)</code></li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">OrderType.GTD (Good Till Date)</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>GTC gibi ama tarih limiti var</li>
            <li>Maker → 0 fee</li>
            <li>Ekstra parametre: <code>expiration</code> (unix timestamp)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">OrderType.FOK (Fill or Kill)</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>Market order — tamami aninda dolsun yoksa iptal</li>
            <li>Taker → fee odenir</li>
            <li><code>create_and_post_market_order(args, OrderType.FOK)</code></li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">OrderType.FAK (Fill and Kill)</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>Market order — ne kadar dolarsa o kadar, kalan iptal</li>
            <li>Taker → fee odenir</li>
            <li><code>create_and_post_market_order(args, OrderType.FAK)</code></li>
            <li>Polymarket'in IOC (Immediate or Cancel) karsiligi</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <!-- BOLUM 8: Fee Yapisi -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-red);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">8. Fee Yapisi</h2>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Formul</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">fee = shares × feeRate × price × (1 - price)</pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Fee Rate'ler</h3>
        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Kategori</th>
                    <th>feeRate</th>
                    <th>Max fee (p=0.50)</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Crypto</td>
                    <td>0.072</td>
                    <td>%3.6</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Sports</td>
                    <td>0.030</td>
                    <td>%1.5</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Finance/Politics</td>
                    <td>0.040</td>
                    <td>%2.0</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Geopolitics</td>
                    <td>0</td>
                    <td>Bedava</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="docs-info">
            <strong>Bilgi:</strong> Fee sadece taker orderlardan alinir. Maker orderlar (GTC/GTD) bedavadir. Fee, fiyat 0.50'ye yakinken en yuksek, uclara (0 veya 1) yakinken duser.
        </div>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Ornek: 100 share, 0.50 fiyat, crypto</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">fee = 100 × 0.072 × 0.50 × 0.50 = $1.80</pre>
    </div>

