    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <!-- BOLUM 10: Traxon'da Kullanim -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-green);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">10. Traxon'da Kullanim</h2>
        <p>Traxon Python signing service (<code>scripts/polymarket-signer/signing_service.py</code>) bu SDK'yi soyle kullaniyor:</p>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Flask HTTP Sunucusu (port 5099)</h3>
        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Endpoint</th>
                    <th>Metod</th>
                    <th>SDK Karsiligi</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>/health</code></td>
                    <td>GET</td>
                    <td><code>get_ok()</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>/create-and-post</code></td>
                    <td>POST</td>
                    <td><code>create_and_post_order()</code> veya <code>create_and_post_market_order()</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>/cancel</code></td>
                    <td>POST</td>
                    <td><code>cancel()</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>/balance</code></td>
                    <td>GET</td>
                    <td><code>get_balance_allowance()</code></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Order Akisi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">.NET Worker sinyali uretir
    ↓
PolymarketEngine.OpenPositionAsync()
    ↓
HTTP POST http://127.0.0.1:5099/create-and-post
    { token_id, amount, side: "BUY", order_type: "FAK" }
    ↓
Python signing_service.py:
    ├─ MarketOrderArgs olustur
    ├─ client.create_and_post_market_order() → EIP-712 imzala + gonder
    └─ orderId dondur
    ↓
.NET trade'i DB'ye kaydeder</pre>
    </div>
    </div>
</div>

